        .body__center__features__info__1
          %img.body__center__features__info__1__picture{:alt => "", :src => "/assets/sale.png"}/
          .body__center__features__info__1__word
            毎日がセール！
          .body__center__features__info__1__explain
            怒涛のセールラッシュ
